Source of truth (read from `.ai-rules/`):

- `architecture.md`
- `api.md`
- `database.md`
- `security.md`
- `testing.md`
- `workers.md`

OnTrack-specific:

- `docs/specs/api-contract.md` — frontend JSON contract
- `docs/archive/completed-migrations/backend-migration/AUTH_COMPATIBILITY.md` — JWT and OAuth parity
- During migration: do not break Flask until FastAPI passes contract tests
